ctx: intros l l' Hl Hl' Hgt Hge.
exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 1 branch or a conjunctive pattern made of 2 patterns.

original: intros l l' Hl Hl' Hgt Hge. induction l as [|e es IH]. -- simpl. auto. -- simpl. destruct Hl as [Hl_1 Hl_2]. split. ++ intros e' [He' | He']. +++ subst. apply Hgt; intuition. +++ apply Hl_1. auto. ++ apply IH; auto. intros e'' e He H'e''. apply Hge; intuition.
